  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p>\r\n<p>Get all your ingredients and equipment ready</p>\r\n<p>Skim through these steps</p>\r\n<p>Wash your fruit and veg</p>\r\n<p>Note: equipment and pan sizes vary. Ensure you cook food thoroughly (even if it takes you a little longer than 10 mins)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/10-min-feta-asparagus-and-lentil-salad/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p>\r\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a matching lid&nbsp;over a medium heat</p>\r\n<p>Meanwhile, chop the&nbsp;<strong>asparagus&nbsp;</strong>in half (chop them in one bunch for speed!)</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/10-min-feta-asparagus-and-lentil-salad/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the&nbsp;<strong>asparagus&nbsp;</strong>to the pan with a pinch of&nbsp;<strong>salt&nbsp;</strong>and a small splash of&nbsp;<strong>cold&nbsp;water&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Cover and cook for 3-4 min or until bright green and tender with a slight bite</p>\r\n<p>Once done, remove the pan from the heat and set aside until serving</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/10-min-feta-asparagus-and-lentil-salad/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the<strong>&nbsp;baby plum tomatoes&nbsp;</strong>in half</p>\r\n<p>Add the&nbsp;<strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>washed&nbsp;rocket&nbsp;</strong>to a large mixing bowl</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/10-min-feta-asparagus-and-lentil-salad/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Microwave</strong> the <strong>beluga lentils</strong> according to packet instructions</p>\r\n<p>Tip: if you're cooking two packets, pop them in together but increase the microwave cook time accordingly!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/10-min-feta-asparagus-and-lentil-salad/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, crumble the <strong>feta cheese</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p>\r\n<p>Combine the&nbsp;<strong>Dijon mustard</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, the juice of 1/2&nbsp;<span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span><strong>&nbsp;lemon&nbsp;</strong>and 3 tbsp&nbsp;<span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]&nbsp;</span><strong>olive oil</strong></p>\r\n<p>Season with a pinch of&nbsp;<strong>salt</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>pepper </strong>&ndash;&nbsp;this is your&nbsp;<strong>lemony dressing&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/10-min-feta-asparagus-and-lentil-salad/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cooked lentils</strong> to the bowl of <strong>tomatoes</strong> and <strong>rocket</strong> with the<strong> lemony dressing</strong> and give everything a good mix up &ndash; this is your<strong> lentil salad</strong></p>\r\n<p>Cut the remaining <strong>lemon</strong> into wedges</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/10-min-feta-asparagus-and-lentil-salad/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Set the <strong>lentil salad</strong> in the centre of the table, ready to share</p>\r\n<p>Top with the <strong>asparagus</strong>,<strong>&nbsp;crumbled feta</strong>,<strong> pumpkin seeds&nbsp;</strong>and&nbsp;<strong>lemon wedges</strong></p>\r\n<p>Season with a grind of<strong> black pepper </strong>and let everyone dig in</p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
